======================
ABOUT
======================

Auto Banner: an advertising plug-in for Joomla! content management system.

Adding advertising banners manually to every article in large websites can be complex and require a lot of time and effort. 
Auto Banner facilitates this task by automating the process and providing a user-friendly banner management interface.

======================
SPECIFICATIONS
======================

Version: 1.0
Last updated: 18 01 2010
Size: 10.9 Kb
Plug-in Type: Content
Joomla! version: 1.5

======================
REQUIREMENTS
======================

Requires default Joomla! com_banners component and module.

